readable.content: People , possibly fishermen , with their boats in shadow on shore at an orangesunset A man in an orange vest is standing next to a yellow canoe . People tend canoes at the edge of a body of water during a dimly lit time of day . The men are getting their kayaks secured on the beach for the night . Two men standing on the shore beside their kayaks at dusk .
